  "texts": [
    "A search strategy was developed, including variations of the terms generative AI and diagnosis.",
    "The search strategy was as follows: articles in English that included the words \"large language model\", \"LLM\", \"generative artificial intelligence\", \"generative AI\", \"generative pre-trained transformers\" 1, \"GPT\", \"Bing\", \"Prometheus\", \"Bard\", \"PaLM\" 6, 7, \"Pathways Language Model\", \"LaMDA\" 8, \"Language Model for Dialogue Applications\", \"Llama\" 4, 5, or \"Large Language Model Meta AI\" and also \"diagnosis\", \"diagnostic\", \"quiz\", \"examination\", or \"vignette\" were included.",
    "We searched the following electronic databases for literature from June 2018 through December 2023:",
    "Medline, Scopus, Web of Science, Cochrane Central, and MedRxiv.",
    "June 2018 represents when the first generative AI model was published."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
